                "text_pyDJT6": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Retro Chroma was started by two friends drawn to home objects with texture, a sense of time, and a touch of playfulness.<br/><br/>We look for pieces that feel lived-in rather than mass-produced — lamps, textiles, and small objects that can shift the mood of an everyday corner.<br/><br/>Some come from small workshops. Some are shaped by hand. All are chosen for the character they bring into everyday spaces.</p>",
